Main Street Inbound

Description:

The Main Street Inbound leaves the University Downtown Center and travels through Main Street in Binghamton & Johnson City and the Pharmacy & Nursing Schools enroute to campus.


Reminder: All Inbound buses at the University Downtown Center return to campus.

Operation Time:

Weekdays:
7:40 A.M. to 10:45 P.M.


Weekends:
Limited Saturday evening service - see schedule below.

For service to Main Street in Johnson City please take the Westside Inbound, and transfer at Floral Av & Main Street for a BC Transit Route 35 Outbound.
For service to Main Street in Binghamton please take the Westside Inbound.
